(GASPS)

226
00:14:25,594 --> 00:14:27,283
哎呀呀！
Mine are black, too!

227
00:14:27,283 --> 00:14:29,243
哎呀呀！
Ah…

228
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:34,374
看样子是煤煤虫在作怪

229
00:14:34,415 --> 00:14:35,416
煤煤虫？

230
00:14:35,666 --> 00:14:38,377
你说的煤煤虫是不是会
You've got soot sprites in your house.

231
00:14:38,377 --> 00:14:40,254
〝哇啦哇啦〞的乱跑啊
Soot sprites? The black puff balls? About this big?

232
00:14:40,254 --> 00:14:42,173
是啊
Soot sprites? The black puff balls? About this big?

233
00:14:42,173 --> 00:14:44,008
它们专门跑到没人住的旧房子里
They scurry everywhere when you enter a room?

234
00:14:44,008 --> 00:14:45,676
它们专门跑到没人住的旧房子里
That's right.

235
00:14:45,676 --> 00:14:49,326
然后弄得满屋子的灰尘和煤灰
They live in old, empty houses

236
00:14:49,326 --> 00:14:53,976
我小时候也有看过
and run all over the place, covering everything with dirt.

237
00:14:54,143 --> 00:14:57,542
想不到妳们也看到
I used to be able to see them when I was your age.

238
00:14:57,542 --> 00:15:00,754
婆婆，它们是妖怪吗？
So you've seen them, too. That's very interesting.

239
00:15:00,754 --> 00:15:04,132
其实也没什么好怕的
So they're a kind of ghost, then?

240
00:15:04,132 --> 00:15:07,490
只要对它们笑笑　它们就不会害人
Don't worry, dear. They're nothing to be afraid of.

241
00:15:07,490 --> 00:15:11,160
住上一阵子之后　它们自然就会不见
If they decide you're nice people, they won't harm you,

242
00:15:11,202 --> 00:15:13,412
说不定它们已经在天花板上　讨论该搬去哪里了
and after a while, they'll just go away.

243
00:15:13,412 --> 00:15:15,623
说不定它们已经在天花板上　讨论该搬去哪里了
I bet they're up in the rafters right now,

244
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:20,211
having a talk about whether or not they should move out.

245
00:15:20,378 --> 00:15:23,214
小美，它们很快就会不见了
(JABBERING)

246
00:15:23,256 --> 00:15:24,257
不好玩

247
00:15:24,298 --> 00:15:26,321
可是要是来这么一大堆　该怎么办？
- Hear that, Mei? They're gonna move out.    - I don't want them to leave.

248
00:15:26,321 --> 00:15:28,260
人家才不怕那些
- Hear that, Mei? They're gonna move out.    - I don't want them to leave.

249
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,325
是吗？
What if a huge one came chasing after you?

250
00:15:30,325 --> 00:15:31,743
那以后晚上　姐姐就不陪妳上厕所
What if a huge one came chasing after you?

251
00:15:31,743 --> 00:15:32,432
So what? I'm not afraid.

252
00:15:32,598 --> 00:15:34,579
Right. Then you can go to the bathroom

253
00:15:34,579 --> 00:15:36,915
来来⋯快来打扫吧
by yourself in the middle of the night.

254
00:15:36,915 --> 00:15:38,145
妳们去河边打点水回来吧
(LAUGHING)

255
00:15:38,145 --> 00:15:39,668
妳们去河边打点水回来吧
Come on, girls.

256
00:15:39,668 --> 00:15:41,524
河边啊
Let's get to work. Who'd like to fetch some water for the pump?

257
00:15:41,524 --> 00:15:43,401
人家也要去
Let's get to work. Who'd like to fetch some water for the pump?

258
00:15:43,568 --> 00:15:44,777
I'll go get it.

259
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:46,841
小美，妳在一边等着
I'll go, too!

260
00:15:46,841 --> 00:15:48,739
小美，妳在一边等着
(LAUGHING)

261
00:15:49,407 --> 00:15:52,201
Mei, wait there, okay?

262
00:15:57,206 --> 00:16:03,337
有没有抓到鱼？
Did you catch a fish?

263
00:16:09,469 --> 00:16:12,680
婆婆，有水了
(GRUNTING)

264
00:16:12,847 --> 00:16:14,765
好好打啊
(SQUEALING)

265
00:16:14,765 --> 00:16:17,268
打到水变凉为止
Granny, the pump's working!

266
00:16:17,268 --> 00:16:19,270
好
Keep pumping!

267
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:21,439
Don't stop until the water gets cold.

268
00:16:21,606 --> 00:16:22,899
Okay.

269
00:16:23,107 --> 00:16:25,109
(LAUGHING)

270
00:17:01,437 --> 00:17:04,440
你不是刚刚那个吗？　有事吗

271
00:17:05,024 --> 00:17:08,381
我妈妈要给婆婆的
Oh. Hello again. Can I help you?

272
00:17:08,381 --> 00:17:12,198
是什么？
Eh… My… mom said to give this to Granny.

273
00:17:13,616 --> 00:17:15,076
Oh. What is it?

274
00:17:17,411 --> 00:17:19,413
等等，这是什么啊
- Mmm.    - Hmm?

275
00:17:19,413 --> 00:17:20,644
Mmm! Eh…

276
00:17:20,644 --> 00:17:22,875
是勘太吗？
Hey, wait! What is this?

277
00:17:23,376 --> 00:17:28,339
你们家是可怕的大鬼屋
Is that Kanta?

278
00:17:28,339 --> 00:17:30,967
勘太！
Hey, you in there!

279
00:17:30,967 --> 00:17:34,554
勘太！
- Your house is haunted!    - Kanta!

280
00:17:37,473 --> 00:17:38,683
Mmm.

281
00:17:39,016 --> 00:17:41,477
爸爸以前也这样作弄过女生
(MEI GIGGLES)

282
00:17:41,477 --> 00:17:43,938
爸爸以前也这样作弄过女生
(LAUGHING)

283
00:17:44,105 --> 00:17:46,691
男生最讨人厌了
Satsuki, I acted just like that when I was a boy.

284
00:17:46,691 --> 00:17:48,422
不过　婆婆这个糯米团很好吃
Satsuki, I acted just like that when I was a boy.

285
00:17:48,422 --> 00:17:51,237
那便多吃点啊
I hate boys, but I'm glad he brought this cake you made.

286
00:17:51,237 --> 00:17:52,279
It's great, Granny.

287
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,989
婆婆，谢谢您的糯米团
(KUSAKABE LAUGHS)

288
00:17:53,989 --> 00:17:55,491
Eat all you like.

289
00:17:55,658 --> 00:17:56,784
SATSUKI: Thanks, moving man!

290
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:59,703
真是太谢谢您了
MEI: Thanks, moving man!

291
00:17:59,703 --> 00:18:02,331
婆婆再见
Thanks for everything, Granny.

292
00:18:03,541 --> 00:18:05,751
- Good-bye, Granny!    - Good-bye, Granny!

293
00:18:14,176 --> 00:18:16,846
(CHOPPING)

294
00:18:27,773 --> 00:18:31,068
(WOOD CLATTERING)

295
00:18:31,193 --> 00:18:34,030
(LEAVES RUSTLING)

296
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:42,204
(WIND HOWLING)

297
00:18:42,371 --> 00:18:44,081
(SCREAMING)

298
00:18:51,672 --> 00:18:55,760
(WIND WHISTLING)

299
00:19:08,314 --> 00:19:11,275
(CREAKING)

300
00:19:11,525 --> 00:19:14,111
(POTS RATTLING)

301
00:19:16,405 --> 00:19:20,013
爸爸，我们家　破破烂烂的会否倒下来

302
00:19:20,013 --> 00:19:22,557
要是才刚搬来就倒塌　那可怎么得了
Dad, this house is too old. I think it's gonna fall down.

303
00:19:22,557 --> 00:19:25,373
要是才刚搬来就倒塌　那可怎么得了
(LAUGHING)

304
00:19:25,414 --> 00:19:28,668
That would be a problem, since we just moved in here.

305
00:19:28,834 --> 00:19:29,669
(LOUD CRASH)

306
00:19:29,877 --> 00:19:30,836
Huh?

307
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:39,053
(SHUTTERS RATTLING)

308
00:19:44,350 --> 00:19:47,895
(CLOCK TICKING)

309
00:19:49,146 --> 00:19:50,940
(HOOTING)

310
00:19:51,107 --> 00:19:53,025
(GASPS)

311
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:57,238
(HOOTING CONTINUES)

312
00:19:59,323 --> 00:20:01,367
我们一起大笑看看
(LAUGHING)

313
00:20:01,367 --> 00:20:03,411
可怕的东西就会跑光
(LAUGHING)

314
00:20:03,452 --> 00:20:07,226
人家才不怕呢！
Everybody, try laughing. Then whatever scares you will go away.

315
00:20:07,226 --> 00:20:08,811
人家才不怕呢！
(LAUGHING)

316
00:20:08,811 --> 00:20:10,626
人家才不怕呢！
But, Dad, I'm not scared.

317
00:20:10,793 --> 00:20:12,294
(LAUGHING)

318
00:20:12,461 --> 00:20:14,338
What? I'm not scared.

319
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,674
(LAUGHING)

320
00:20:17,007 --> 00:20:19,093
(ROARING)

321
00:20:19,260 --> 00:20:21,220
(SHOUTING)

322
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:25,182
(LAUGHING)

323
00:20:54,253 --> 00:20:57,381
一、二、一、二、一、二

324
00:20:57,423 --> 00:20:59,383
很好，加油
BOTH: One, two, one, two, one, two.

325
00:20:59,383 --> 00:21:01,093
用力，加把劲
BOTH: One, two, one, two, one, two.

326
00:21:01,093 --> 00:21:04,054
That's it. Stamp that dirt out, girls. That's it.

327
00:21:06,348 --> 00:21:11,771
好了　衣服都洗好了
Okay. That's all the chores.

328
00:21:11,937 --> 00:21:14,815
- You're done.    - BOTH: Yay!

329
00:21:18,402 --> 00:21:24,283
出发了！
Ready? Hold on!

330
00:21:25,785 --> 00:21:28,162
Who-o-oa!

331
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:30,956
(GIRLS SHRIEKING)

332
00:21:31,123 --> 00:21:33,042
KUSAKABE: Whoo-ooo!

333
00:21:37,463 --> 00:21:40,341
婆婆

334
00:21:40,508 --> 00:21:42,551
您好！
SATSUKI: Granny!

335
00:21:42,551 --> 00:21:44,574
您可真忙啊
SATSUKI: Granny!

336
00:21:44,574 --> 00:21:47,765
三个一起出门啊？
GIRLS: Hi, Granny! KUSAKABE: Good afternoon!

337
00:21:47,765 --> 00:21:50,705
我们要去医院看妈妈
Hello there, Kusakabes! Where are you headed?

338
00:21:50,705 --> 00:21:53,812
可有好一段路呢
We're going to visit Mom at the hospital!

339
00:21:53,812 --> 00:21:55,397
替我帮妳们妈妈问好
That's good! Say hi!

340
00:21:55,397 --> 00:21:57,232
好的
That's good! Say hi!

341
00:21:57,232 --> 00:21:59,401
Tell her I hope she's feeling better.

342
00:21:59,568 --> 00:22:00,653
SATSUKI: We will!

343
00:22:01,987 --> 00:22:04,198
- Mmm.    - Mmm.

344
00:22:13,415 --> 00:22:19,421
走这边！走这边！
Hey, this way. Whoa!

345
00:22:19,588 --> 00:22:21,131
(GIRLS GIGGLING)

346
00:22:34,728 --> 00:22:37,731
Hey, Dad. There it is.

347
00:22:42,403 --> 00:22:43,404
大家好

348
00:22:43,445 --> 00:22:46,323
妳好
(DOOR OPENS)

349
00:22:46,365 --> 00:22:46,928
妈妈！

350
00:22:46,928 --> 00:22:50,223
小美妳也来啦
- Good afternoon, ma'am.    - Hello, dear.

351
00:22:50,223 --> 00:22:53,080
爸爸还走错路呢
- Mommy!    - Hi, Mei. It's so good to see you.

352
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,081
真的吗

353
00:22:54,081 --> 00:22:55,895
妳也来啦
Daddy kept getting lost the whole way here, Mom.

354
00:22:55,895 --> 00:22:56,958
今天田里休息一天

355
00:22:56,958 --> 00:22:58,857
是啊
Oh, he did? No school?

356
00:22:58,857 --> 00:23:01,275
爸爸正在跟医生说话
No, it's a rice-planting day.

357
00:23:01,275 --> 00:23:03,027
妈妈很高兴你们都来了
Oh, is that so?

358
00:23:03,027 --> 00:23:04,592
妈妈很高兴你们都来了
Hey, Mom, Dad's talking to the doctor.

359
00:23:04,592 --> 00:23:05,259
新家怎么样啦

360
00:23:05,259 --> 00:23:07,636
都整理好了没？
I am so happy to see you girls.

361
00:23:07,803 --> 00:23:10,556
So how do you like it in the country? Have you settled in?

362
00:23:10,723 --> 00:23:14,560
甚么？我们家是鬼屋啊
- Yeah.    - Hmm?

363
00:23:14,727 --> 00:23:17,062
妈妈喜欢住鬼屋吗？
Mei's scared…

364
00:23:17,062 --> 00:23:18,480
当然啰
- A haunted house?    - Mmm-hmm.

365
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,878
妈妈真想快点出院　看看鬼长什么样子
Mommy, do you like haunted houses?

366
00:23:20,878 --> 00:23:21,567
小美太好了

367
00:23:21,567 --> 00:23:24,591
我好担心啊
Of course. I'll have to get better soon so I can meet some ghosts.

368
00:23:24,591 --> 00:23:26,843
因为我好怕　妈妈会不喜欢那里
- See that, Mei?    - Mmm-hmm.

369
00:23:26,843 --> 00:23:27,447
那妳们两个呢？

370
00:23:27,447 --> 00:23:30,033
喜欢
Mei was worried that you wouldn't come home if the house was haunted.

371
00:23:30,033 --> 00:23:31,118
妈妈我不怕鬼

372
00:23:31,118 --> 00:23:32,953
- Do you two like it?    - Yeah!

373
00:23:33,078 --> 00:23:34,934
小美的头发都是妳梳的？
I'm not scared at all.

374
00:23:34,934 --> 00:23:36,790
小美的头发都是妳梳的？
(LAUGHS)

375
00:23:36,957 --> 00:23:39,188
梳得真好
Oh, what cute hair. Did you do this, Satsuki?

376
00:23:39,188 --> 00:23:40,231
要好好谢姐姐啊！小美

377
00:23:40,231 --> 00:23:43,339
可是姐姐动不动就生气
- Mmm-hmm.    - It's very nice, huh, Mei?

378
00:23:43,339 --> 00:23:45,424
还不都是因为妳不乖
- What a lucky girl you are.    - Yeah, but she yells at me a lot.

379
00:23:45,424 --> 00:23:47,363
小月，过来让妈妈看看
- What a lucky girl you are.    - Yeah, but she yells at me a lot.

380
00:23:47,363 --> 00:23:50,554
你的头发会不会太短了
- That's because you never sit still.    - Let's see your hair, Satsuki.

381
00:23:50,554 --> 00:23:51,013
我喜欢这个样子

382
00:23:51,055 --> 00:23:52,994
人家也要！人家也要！
You sure it isn't a little too short?

383
00:23:52,994 --> 00:23:54,579
排队！
No, I like it this way, Mom.

384
00:23:54,579 --> 00:23:56,581
头发还是一样经常打结
- Brush my hair! Brush mine!    - Wait your turn, Mei.

385
00:23:56,581 --> 00:23:58,770
就跟妈妈小时候一样
- Brush my hair! Brush mine!    - Wait your turn, Mei.

386
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:00,648
那我长大以后
Your hair will never cooperate.

387
00:24:00,814 --> 00:24:03,150
头发会不会　变得跟妈妈的一样呢？
It's exactly like my hair when I was your age.

388
00:24:03,317 --> 00:24:05,173
应该会吧
Do you think it will start cooperating soon?

389
00:24:05,173 --> 00:24:07,446
因为妳跟妈妈最像了
I want it to look like yours.

390
00:24:07,446 --> 00:24:07,988
(CHUCKLES)

391
00:24:08,113 --> 00:24:09,573
I think it will.

392
00:24:09,740 --> 00:24:11,659
You and I are a lot alike, Satsuki.

393
00:24:19,667 --> 00:24:22,461
(INAUDIBLE)

394
00:24:25,422 --> 00:24:27,383
妈妈好像好了很多

395
00:24:27,424 --> 00:24:28,425
是啊

396
00:24:28,509 --> 00:24:31,929
医生也说　再过不久就可以出院了
- Mom looked great, didn't she, Dad?    - Yeah, she did,

397
00:24:31,929 --> 00:24:33,826
再过不久，明天吗？
her doctor said she should be able to come home real soon.

398
00:24:33,826 --> 00:24:35,849
妳什么都是明天
her doctor said she should be able to come home real soon.

399
00:24:35,849 --> 00:24:38,644
明天可能有点难
- So she'll be home tomorrow?    - There she goes again with tomorrow.

400
00:24:38,644 --> 00:24:40,646
可是人家好想要跟妈妈一起睡
- So she'll be home tomorrow?    - There she goes again with tomorrow.

401
00:24:40,646 --> 00:24:41,605
Well, I think tomorrow might be a bit soon.

402
00:24:41,605 --> 00:24:45,526
妳不是说妳已经长大　要自己一个人睡的吗？
Mom said she was gonna sleep in my bed with me.

403
00:24:45,651 --> 00:24:48,236
跟妈妈睡没关系
I thought you weren't scared to sleep alone.

404
00:24:48,236 --> 00:24:49,738
Can't you sleep by yourself?

405
00:24:49,863 --> 00:24:51,407
She's the one who's scared, not me.

406
00:24:51,532 --> 00:24:54,034
(BOTH LAUGHING)

407
00:25:09,508 --> 00:25:11,343
爸爸

408
00:25:11,552 --> 00:25:17,015
天亮了
Hey, Dad! Look, it's morning!

409
00:25:17,015 --> 00:25:19,727
起床！
(GROANING)

410
00:25:19,852 --> 00:25:23,230
- Umph!    - Hey, wake up!

411
00:25:23,397 --> 00:25:26,400
对不起，爸爸又睡过头
(GROANING)

412
00:25:26,483 --> 00:25:28,464
今天开始要带便当

413
00:25:28,464 --> 00:25:31,780
糟糕，爸爸忘记了
- Sorry. I overslept again.    - I have to take lunch to school today.

414
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:33,010
没关系，我也帮你们做好了
Oh, no. I forgot all about that.

415
00:25:33,010 --> 00:25:34,908
烧焦了
Oh, no. I forgot all about that.

416
00:25:34,908 --> 00:25:37,411
马上来
That's okay. I'm making lunch for everyone.

417
00:25:37,578 --> 00:25:41,373
这是小美的
- Hey, it's burning!    - I'm coming. Just a minute.

418
00:25:41,457 --> 00:25:42,916
我的

419
00:25:42,916 --> 00:25:45,335
小美，坐下来好好吃饭
I'm making this one for you, Mei.

420
00:25:45,335 --> 00:25:47,567
来
I get one?

421
00:25:47,567 --> 00:25:49,944
便当自己包好
Mei, sit down and eat.

422
00:25:49,944 --> 00:25:52,718
There you go. Wrap it up so it stays fresh. Okay?

423
00:25:52,718 --> 00:25:55,804
小月
(SIGHS)

424
00:25:55,804 --> 00:26:00,768
糟了，来啊
- Satsuki!    - That's Michiko.

425
00:26:00,934 --> 00:26:03,312
这么快就交到朋友啦？
Hi!

426
00:26:03,395 --> 00:26:05,167
叫得很真亲密呢

427
00:26:05,167 --> 00:26:06,982
她叫小满
So, you made a friend already, did you?

428
00:26:07,066 --> 00:26:11,236
我吃饱了
- Satsuki, time for school!    - She's walking to school with me.

429
00:26:11,236 --> 00:26:12,800
(SLURPING)

430
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,406
我去上学了
I gotta go.

