544
00:37:12,939 --> 00:37:15,525
嘴巴是这样子的
Mmm-hmm. But he called himself Totoro.

545
00:37:15,567 --> 00:37:17,506
有这么小的
He was furry, with a great big mouth.

546
00:37:17,506 --> 00:37:19,446
还有这么大的
He was furry, with a great big mouth.

547
