Quit laughing! I really did see Totoro!

572
00:38:27,764 --> 00:38:29,057
I'm not lying.

573
00:38:29,224 --> 00:38:30,642
Mmm.

574
00:38:34,479 --> 00:38:36,397
小美啊

575
00:38:36,439 --> 00:38:39,546
人家没有骗你们
Mei?

576
00:38:39,546 --> 00:38:41,194
其实爸爸跟姐姐
It's not a lie, Dad.

577
00:38:41,194 --> 00:38:42,445
也没有认为妳在骗人啊
It's not a lie, Dad.

578
00:38:42,445 --> 00:38:43,759
Hmm. Don't worry, Mei.

579
00:38:43,759 --> 00:38:47,304
小美刚才一定是　遇到了森林的主人
Satsuki and I believe you, and I bet you I know what happened.

580
00:38:47,304 --> 00:38:50,203
这就表示小美运气很好
You must have met one of the spirits of the forest.

581
00:38:50,203 --> 00:38:53,372
不过这种机会并不常有
That means you're a very lucky girl.

582
00:38:53,372 --> 00:38:56,063
来，我们去跟它打个招呼吧
But you can't always see the spirits.

583
00:38:56,063 --> 00:38:57,815
打招呼？
You can only see them when they want you to.

584
00:38:57,815 --> 00:39:00,421
