But, Dad, I want to see them, too.

604
00:40:06,112 --> 00:40:08,406
这棵树真大啊
Maybe you will, if you're lucky.

605
00:40:09,449 --> 00:40:12,535
一定是从很久很久以前
Mmm. Magnificent tree.

606
00:40:12,619 --> 00:40:15,496
