613
00:40:29,031 --> 00:40:31,053
该吃饭了
And I think it will make your mother feel right at home.

614
00:40:31,053 --> 00:40:34,036
对了　我跟小满约好要到她家去
So, let's give this tree a nice greeting and go eat our lunch.

615
00:40:34,036 --> 00:40:34,870
人家也要去

616
00:40:34,870 --> 00:40:37,205
立正站好！
Then I want to write a letter to Mom and tell her all about this.

617
00:40:37,205 --> 00:40:39,082
多谢您照顾我们家小美
- I will, too!    - Attention!

618
00:40:39,082 --> 00:40:40,980
从今以后还盼您多多关照
- I will, too!    - Attention!

619
