她一直吵着　要到姐姐那边去所以⋯
- Granny, what's wrong?    - I don't know.

653
00:42:50,609 --> 00:42:52,507
可是
- Granny, what's wrong?    - I don't know.

654
00:42:52,507 --> 00:42:54,405
小美
She said she wouldn't stop crying unless I brought her to you.

655
00:42:54,405 --> 00:42:56,199
今天是爸爸　要到大学去教课的日子
She said she wouldn't stop crying unless I brought her to you.

656
