You know you had to stay with Granny.

658
00:43:00,953 --> 00:43:04,540
姊姊还要再上两个小时的课
I have school and Dad's teaching at the university.

659
00:43:04,582 --> 00:43:07,626
婆婆的田里又那么忙
I only have two more hours of school to go.

660
00:43:07,626 --> 00:43:09,607
小美在婆婆的家里一直都很乖的
I only have two more hours of school to go.

661
00:43:09,607 --> 00:43:11,047
Can't you just stay with Granny until then?

662
00:43:11,255 --> 00:43:14,342
She's been so good up till now. Weren't you, Mei?

663
00:43:19,514 --> 00:43:22,767
婆婆，那我去跟老师说说看
(SIGHS)

664
00:43:22,975 --> 00:43:25,853
Well, I'll talk to my teacher and see what we can do.

665
00:43:27,563 --> 00:43:30,024
现在小月因为妈妈住院
(LAUGHING)

666
00:43:30,024 --> 00:43:32,109
所以妹妹暂时没人照顾
(LAUGHING)

667
00:43:32,109 --> 00:43:34,090
同学们要好好跟她相处啊
Satsuki's mom is in the hospital,

668
00:43:34,090 --> 00:43:37,240
好、好
so her sister Mei is going to stay with us today, okay, class?

669
00:43:37,406 --> 00:43:43,538
这是什么啊
- Let's make her feel welcome.    - ALL: Yes, ma'am.

670
00:43:43,621 --> 00:43:45,540
大龙猫呀

671
00:43:46,290 --> 00:43:49,544
不要吵
- What are you drawing, Mei?    - It's a big Totoro.

672
00:43:49,627 --> 00:43:52,588
Shh. Mei, try to keep quiet, will you?

673
00:43:52,713 --> 00:43:55,049
Mmm-hmm.

674
00:43:55,216 --> 00:43:56,092
(SIGHS)

675
00:43:56,676 --> 00:44:00,033
再见再见，明天见了
(BELL RINGING)

676
00:44:00,033 --> 00:44:02,557
再见

677
00:44:02,723 --> 00:44:05,143
我今天不能去社团了
CHILDREN: Bye, Mei!

678
00:44:05,309 --> 00:44:06,727
我去跟老师说
MICHIKO: Come again soon!

679
00:44:06,727 --> 00:44:07,311
再见了

680
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:09,438
拜拜，再见
I have to skip our club meeting, Michiko.

681
00:44:09,480 --> 00:44:12,441
小美，快点，要下雨了
I'll let everyone know. Bye!

682
00:44:13,901 --> 00:44:15,778
Hurry up, Mei. It's gonna rain.

683
00:44:15,945 --> 00:44:17,071
Okay.

684
00:44:20,700 --> 00:44:21,909
下雨了

685
00:44:24,912 --> 00:44:27,748
- Ah! Here it comes!    - Here it comes!

686
00:44:33,129 --> 00:44:34,338
(SPLAT)

687
00:44:34,505 --> 00:44:36,007
(GASPS)

688
00:44:38,843 --> 00:44:42,597
人家都没有哭，棒不棒？　嗯
Come on.

689
00:44:43,347 --> 00:44:45,766
可是真伤脑筋
I didn't even cry. That's good, huh?

690
00:44:45,766 --> 00:44:48,186
可是真伤脑筋
Hmm.

691
00:44:48,352 --> 00:44:52,523
土地公爷爷　请您让我们躲一下雨
Yeah, but we're not home yet.

692
00:44:52,815 --> 00:44:56,152
We'd like to share your roof for a while, sir, if you don't mind.

693
00:45:31,604 --> 00:45:33,814
- Mmm.    - Huh?

694
00:45:33,981 --> 00:45:38,653
可是⋯
- Don't you…    - Mmm. Mmm!

695
00:45:38,819 --> 00:45:40,112
Mmm!

696
00:45:41,739 --> 00:45:42,907
Hey!

697
00:45:57,588 --> 00:45:59,674
姊姊，有伞子真棒啊

698
00:46:00,591 --> 00:46:04,011
可是伞子顶破了一个大洞
- That was lucky, wasn't it?    - Mmm-hmm.

699
00:46:05,930 --> 00:46:08,808
- MEI: This umbrella has holes.    - Hmm.

700
00:46:12,937 --> 00:46:16,503
爸爸今天好像没带伞
(EATING)

701
00:46:16,503 --> 00:46:18,901
人家也要去接爸爸
(CLOCK CHIMING)

702
00:46:19,068 --> 00:46:20,111
Dad left his umbrella here.

703
00:46:20,278 --> 00:46:23,656
不就是忘记了
- I'd better take it to him.    - I wanna go, too.

704
00:46:24,448 --> 00:46:25,449
明明都已经下雨了

705
00:46:25,491 --> 00:46:27,618
竟然还会傻得忘了带伞　你骗鬼啊！
What? I left it.

706
00:46:27,618 --> 00:46:29,140
好痛啊
(SIGHS)

707
00:46:29,140 --> 00:46:31,851
我看啊　你八成是把伞子弄坏了
What kind of fool forgets his umbrella at school when it's raining?

708
00:46:31,851 --> 00:46:34,667
才不是呢
- Hey!    - I bet you were swinging it around

709
00:46:34,875 --> 00:46:35,835
and you broke it.

710
00:46:36,002 --> 00:46:37,295
No, I didn't.

711
00:46:42,883 --> 00:46:45,011
(GASPS)

712
00:46:45,177 --> 00:46:48,597
有人在家吗？
Ahh.

713
00:46:50,308 --> 00:46:52,372
小月？还有小美
Hello! Is anyone home?

714
00:46:52,372 --> 00:46:54,332
妈
Hello! Is anyone home?

715
00:46:54,332 --> 00:46:56,668
今天真的是麻烦你们了
Oh, Satsuki and Mei. Come in. Granny!

716
00:46:56,668 --> 00:46:59,108
不用客气
Oh, Satsuki and Mei. Come in. Granny!

717
00:46:59,275 --> 00:47:01,006
对了　这是勘太今天借我们的伞
Thanks for watching Mei today.

718
00:47:01,006 --> 00:47:02,632
对了　这是勘太今天借我们的伞
Sorry we couldn't keep her happy.

719
00:47:02,632 --> 00:47:04,530
这孩子⋯
Oh. I wanted to give back this umbrella that Kanta lent us.

720
00:47:04,530 --> 00:47:06,532
这么破的伞子真不好意思
Oh. I wanted to give back this umbrella that Kanta lent us.

721
00:47:06,574 --> 00:47:08,638
这把伞帮了我们好大的忙
What? He lent you this? Oh, my. Look how beat up it is.

722
00:47:08,638 --> 00:47:10,557
不过却害勘太都淋湿了
What? He lent you this? Oh, my. Look how beat up it is.

723
00:47:10,557 --> 00:47:12,621
麻烦伯母谢谢勘太
Mei was walking home from school with me.

724
00:47:12,705 --> 00:47:14,206
不必客气
So, it was really nice of him to help us out. Tell him thank you.

725
00:47:14,206 --> 00:47:15,687
反正他老是弄得全身都是泥
So, it was really nice of him to help us out. Tell him thank you.

726
00:47:15,687 --> 00:47:17,960
淋淋雨反而干净些
- He must have been drenched.    - That's okay.

727
00:47:18,085 --> 00:47:19,983
你们要去接爸爸啊
Kanta is such a dirty kid. He can always use a good drenching.

728
00:47:19,983 --> 00:47:21,881
真是孝顺啊
Kanta is such a dirty kid. He can always use a good drenching.

729
00:47:22,048 --> 00:47:23,799
小美，拜拜
Are you off to meet your dad at the bus stop?

730
00:47:23,799 --> 00:47:26,510
拜拜
- SATSUKI: Yes, he forgot his umbrella.    - Such good kids.

731
00:47:26,677 --> 00:47:28,971
- Bye, girls.    - SATSUKI: Bye!

732
00:47:35,519 --> 00:47:37,021
刚才是谁来了呀
(GIGGLING)

733
00:47:37,188 --> 00:47:39,231
才懒得理呢
(IMITATES AIRPLANE)

734
00:47:39,398 --> 00:47:44,612
刚好赶上
- Who was at the door, Kanta?    - Beats me.

735
00:47:46,447 --> 00:47:48,407
(GASPS) There's the bus, Mei!

736
00:47:57,583 --> 00:47:59,502
你们要坐车吗？

737
00:48:00,503 --> 00:48:02,880
开车
Are you getting on?

738
00:48:04,507 --> 00:48:06,926
Drive on.

739
00:48:10,596 --> 00:48:12,598
爸爸没有搭这班车

740
00:48:12,640 --> 00:48:14,475
一定是搭下一班啦

741
00:48:14,475 --> 00:48:16,685
小美，妳到婆婆家等好不好？
Satsuki, Dad wasn't on the bus.

742
00:48:16,685 --> 00:48:19,021
小美，妳到婆婆家等好不好？
He'll be on the next one for sure.

743
00:48:19,188 --> 00:48:22,483
Do you want to go back to Granny's and wait there?

744
00:48:41,168 --> 00:48:44,255
(WATER DRIPPING)

745
00:48:52,721 --> 00:48:58,686
怎么啦？
What's the matter?

746
00:49:04,150 --> 00:49:08,154
(SQUEAKING)

747
00:49:24,378 --> 00:49:27,506
小美
(SIGHS)

748
00:49:27,673 --> 00:49:29,508
妳困啦

749
00:49:29,675 --> 00:49:32,094
早跟妳说过的嘛
What is it, Mei? Are you sleepy?

750
00:49:32,094 --> 00:49:34,409
要不要先到婆婆家去睡一下？
What is it, Mei? Are you sleepy?

751
00:49:34,409 --> 00:49:37,036
爸爸就快到了　撑着点啊
I knew this would happen. Don't you want to wait at Granny's?

752
00:49:37,036 --> 00:49:39,768
爸爸就快到了　撑着点啊
Mmm-mmm.

753
00:49:39,977 --> 00:49:42,521
It's okay, Mei. He'll be here soon.

754
00:49:44,481 --> 00:49:48,444
巴士怎么这么慢
(SIGHS)

755
00:49:48,611 --> 00:49:50,571
That bus sure is late, huh?

756
00:49:54,533 --> 00:49:55,743
来

757
00:49:58,746 --> 00:50:00,664
Here.

758
00:50:03,375 --> 00:50:05,711
(GRUNTS)

759
00:50:23,062 --> 00:50:25,064
(MOANING)

760
00:50:25,439 --> 00:50:26,398
(GRUNTING)

761
00:50:27,233 --> 00:50:30,194
(FOOTSTEPS)

762
00:50:39,203 --> 00:50:40,329
(GASPS)

763
00:50:57,304 --> 00:50:59,974
(GASPING)

764
00:51:10,317 --> 00:51:14,321
(PLINKING)

765
00:51:19,201 --> 00:51:20,119
大龙猫？

766
00:51:23,247 --> 00:51:24,707
Totoro?

767
00:51:24,832 --> 00:51:26,041
(PLINK)

768
00:51:29,211 --> 00:51:32,715
等我一下
(GRUMBLING)

769
00:51:34,550 --> 00:51:39,805
这个借你
Oh, wait a minute.

770
00:51:40,556 --> 00:51:44,476
快点啊　小美快要掉下来了啦
Here. Try this.

771
00:51:44,560 --> 00:51:46,937
Hurry. Mei's slipping.

772
00:51:48,689 --> 00:51:52,651
要这样子用
(GRUNTS)

773
00:51:52,818 --> 00:51:54,737
Hold it over your head. Like this.

774
00:52:05,164 --> 00:52:07,207
(GIGGLES)

775
00:52:20,054 --> 00:52:21,138
(SPLASH)

776
00:52:28,395 --> 00:52:30,064
(SPLASHING)

777
00:52:32,149 --> 00:52:34,860
(GRUMBLING)

778
00:52:43,661 --> 00:52:46,914
(SPLASHING)

779
00:52:49,708 --> 00:52:52,711
(BELLOWING)

780
00:52:55,923 --> 00:52:56,840
(THUD)

781
00:52:57,007 --> 00:52:57,925
(SHRIEKS)

782
00:52:58,092 --> 00:53:00,094
(DOUSING)

783
00:53:01,970 --> 00:53:05,182
(ROARING)

784
00:53:07,601 --> 00:53:08,706
巴士来了！
(GASPS)

785
00:53:08,706 --> 00:53:09,728
Oh.

786
00:53:11,522 --> 00:53:13,941
Here comes the bus.

787
00:53:15,943 --> 00:53:17,236
BOTH: Huh?

788
00:53:17,403 --> 00:53:20,030
(WIND WHISTLING)

789
00:53:20,447 --> 00:53:22,741
(YOWLING)

790
00:53:29,289 --> 00:53:31,250
(MEOWING)

791
00:53:31,500 --> 00:53:33,419
(GASPING)

792
00:53:34,795 --> 00:53:37,548
(HUMMING)

793
00:53:40,134 --> 00:53:42,010
(BELLOWING)

794
00:53:43,303 --> 00:53:46,432
(WIND WHISTLING)

795
00:54:16,587 --> 00:54:23,719
大龙猫　把爸爸的伞给带走了
Well, Mei, so much for bringing Dad his umbrella.

796
00:54:32,769 --> 00:54:34,688
对不起，对不起

797
00:54:34,771 --> 00:54:36,565
开车

798
00:54:36,607 --> 00:54:38,567
爸爸没搭上电车
- Hi. Sorry I'm late.    - WOMAN: Drive on.

799
00:54:38,567 --> 00:54:40,360
所以就没赶上平常那班巴士
- Hi. Sorry I'm late.    - WOMAN: Drive on.

800
00:54:40,360 --> 00:54:42,446
害你们担心啦
My train was delayed, so I had to wait for the next bus.

801
00:54:42,446 --> 00:54:44,656
出现了，爸爸　真的出现了
My train was delayed, so I had to wait for the next bus.

802
00:54:44,656 --> 00:54:46,721
对呀，还有猫的巴士
Were you worried?

803
00:54:46,721 --> 00:54:48,723
对呀，还有猫的巴士
Totoro came back, Dad! I saw him!

804
00:54:48,723 --> 00:54:51,037
那辆巴士好大啊
We saw a cat bus, too!

805
00:54:51,037 --> 00:54:52,643
眼睛像这样子啊
- What?    - It was huge!

806
00:54:52,643 --> 00:54:54,583
吓死人了
- What?    - It was huge!

807
00:54:54,583 --> 00:54:55,834
With eyes like this.

808
00:54:55,834 --> 00:54:57,627
看到了！　我看到大龙猫了！
- It was great!    - It was great!

809
00:54:57,627 --> 00:54:59,713
看到了！　我看到大龙猫了！
(LAUGHING)

810
00:54:59,713 --> 00:55:01,715
好棒啊
I saw Totoro! I saw him!

811
00:55:01,715 --> 00:55:03,258
好吓人啊
I saw him, too!

812
00:55:03,383 --> 00:55:06,553
(GIRLS LAUGHING)

813
00:55:06,678 --> 00:55:09,473
(CROAKING)

814
00:55:09,640 --> 00:55:11,433
(INSECTS CHIRPING)

815
00:55:16,063 --> 00:55:18,816
- Hey, Dad, pick us up.    - Come on, Dad.

816
00:55:18,982 --> 00:55:19,942
(GRUNTING)

817
00:55:20,067 --> 00:55:23,570
妈妈
(ALL LAUGHING)

818
00:55:23,654 --> 00:55:26,532
我现在心还在蹦蹦乱跳呢

819
00:55:26,615 --> 00:55:29,784
今天真是既吓人又惊奇　又开心的一天
SATSUKI: Dear Mom:

820
00:55:29,784 --> 00:55:33,163
而且大龙猫送给我们的礼物　实在是太棒了
We had such a weird, mysterious, spectacular day.

821
00:55:33,163 --> 00:55:35,541
是一个用竹叶包着
My heart is still pounding.

822
00:55:35,582 --> 00:55:38,335
然后外面再用　龙须草绑着的小包包
Totoro gave us a wonderful present.

823
00:55:38,335 --> 00:55:40,253
我跟小美回家以后打开一看
It was wrapped in a bamboo leaf

824
00:55:40,253 --> 00:55:42,276
发现里面都是橡果子
and tied with a ribbon made of grass.

825
00:55:42,276 --> 00:55:44,758
发现里面都是橡果子
As soon as we got home, we opened it.

826
00:55:44,925 --> 00:55:47,511
It was filled with acorns.

827
00:55:47,678 --> 00:55:48,366
(GASP)

828
00:55:48,366 --> 00:55:50,764
我们想家里院子　变成森林的话一定很棒
Ahh.

829
00:55:50,764 --> 00:55:52,766
所以就把它们洒在院子里
(CHUCKLING)

830
00:55:52,766 --> 00:55:54,747
不过
“We wanted to grow a beautiful forest with the acorns,

831
00:55:54,747 --> 00:55:55,393
它们现在都还没有发芽

832
00:55:55,393 --> 00:55:58,272
所以小美每天都一直在说
so we planted them in your garden out back, but…”

833
00:55:58,397 --> 00:56:01,275
还没发芽，还没发芽
SATSUKI: … they just won't grow. Mei watches them

834
00:56:01,441 --> 00:56:05,091
就好像猴子螃蟹大战　里面那个螃蟹一样啊
all day, every day,

835
00:56:05,091 --> 00:56:05,821
waiting for them to sprout,

836
00:56:05,988 --> 00:56:07,865
it's starting to make her crabby.

837
00:56:08,031 --> 00:56:10,951
Here's a picture of Mei as a crab.

838
00:56:10,951 --> 00:56:13,224
学校很快就要放暑假了
(CHUCKLING)

839
00:56:13,224 --> 00:56:15,017
希望妈妈的病　能够快点好起来好吗？
(CHUCKLING)

840
00:56:15,017 --> 00:56:15,977
Summer vacation is almost here,

841
00:56:15,977 --> 00:56:18,375
小月
and I can't wait to play outside with you.

842
00:56:18,542 --> 00:56:21,128
Please get well soon. Love, Satsuki.

843
00:56:21,295 --> 00:56:23,005
(GIRLS LAUGHING)

844
00:56:24,631 --> 00:56:27,718
要关灯了
Get ready, and… up!

845
00:56:27,718 --> 00:56:28,886
等等
(SHRIEKING)

846
00:56:29,052 --> 00:56:29,970
(LAUGHING)

847
00:56:29,970 --> 00:56:32,889
爸爸，明天会不会发芽？
- Lights out, girls.    - MEI: Wait, Dad.

848
00:56:32,889 --> 00:56:33,473
这个问题呀

849
00:56:33,473 --> 00:56:36,476
我看要问大龙猫才会知道
Do you think that they'll sprout tomorrow?

850
00:56:36,560 --> 00:56:37,686
晚安
I don't know.

851
00:56:37,811 --> 00:56:40,314
You should ask the Totoro. He would know.

852
00:56:40,522 --> 00:56:41,940
Good night, girls.

853
00:56:42,274 --> 00:56:44,109
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)

854
00:56:49,948 --> 00:56:52,075
(BUZZING OF INSECTS)

855
00:57:26,526 --> 00:57:32,157
小美
Mei.

856
00:57:32,324 --> 00:57:34,242
(GROANING)

857
00:57:45,587 --> 00:57:51,802
那是我们种橡果子的地方
That's where we planted the acorns.

858
00:58:06,191 --> 00:58:08,193
(GRUNTING)

859
00:58:08,360 --> 00:58:09,277
(GIGGLING)

860
00:58:10,946 --> 00:58:13,115
(GRUNTING)

861
00:58:13,281 --> 00:58:14,199
(POP)

862
00:58:14,366 --> 00:58:15,409
(GASPING)

863
00:58:15,617 --> 00:58:17,202
(TOTORO GRUNTING)

864
00:58:17,369 --> 00:58:18,370
(POP)

865
00:58:18,495 --> 00:58:22,666
(GRUNTING)

866
00:58:22,833 --> 00:58:25,168
(POPPING)

867
00:58:25,335 --> 00:58:26,795
(GASPING)

868
00:58:26,920 --> 00:58:29,881
(ALL GRUNTING)

869
00:58:30,048 --> 00:58:33,677
ALL: Ahh!

870
00:59:18,597 --> 00:59:25,395
太棒了！
GIRLS: Yay! We did it! We did it!

871
00:59:25,604 --> 00:59:26,813
GIRLS: Yay!

872
00:59:26,938 --> 00:59:27,981
(BELLOWING)

873
00:59:28,148 --> 00:59:30,150
(HUMMING)

874
00:59:38,742 --> 00:59:40,452
(SQUEALING)

875
00:59:49,377 --> 00:59:52,047
(GRUMBLING)

876
00:59:53,340 --> 00:59:55,217
(GASP)

877
00:59:58,637 --> 01:00:01,723
(WHIRRING)

878
01:00:21,493 --> 01:00:24,496
(ROARING)

879
01:00:25,872 --> 01:00:30,210
(GIRLS ROARING)

880
01:00:32,629 --> 01:00:34,131
(ROARING)

881
01:00:37,634 --> 01:00:41,054
小美，我们都变成风了啊
(GRUMBLING)

882
01:00:42,180 --> 01:00:44,641
Mei, we're the wind!

883
01:01:00,031 --> 01:01:02,159
(INHALES)

884
01:01:02,367 --> 01:01:05,537
(INSTRUMENT PLAYS)

885
01:01:13,461 --> 01:01:17,674
(SECOND INSTRUMENT PLAYS)

886
01:01:19,551 --> 01:01:24,139
(ALL MAKING MUSIC)

887
01:01:35,192 --> 01:01:38,403
Mmm…

888
01:01:38,570 --> 01:01:39,529
(GASPS)

889
01:01:40,822 --> 01:01:45,285
大树不见了
(GROANS)

890
01:01:45,410 --> 01:01:46,661
Where'd the tree go?

891
01:01:47,495 --> 01:01:51,708
成功了！
- Ahh!    - Ahh!

892
01:01:52,042 --> 01:01:53,710
好像在作梦
They're growing! We did it!

893
01:01:53,793 --> 01:01:54,836
却又不是梦
We did it!

894
01:01:54,920 --> 01:01:56,213
好像在作梦
(LAUGHING)

895
01:01:56,630 --> 01:01:57,714
却又不是梦

896
01:01:57,756 --> 01:01:58,735
万岁！

897
01:01:58,735 --> 01:02:01,384
好啊！
SATSUKI: I thought it was a dream! MEI: But it wasn't!

898
01:02:01,551 --> 01:02:05,889
BOTH: I thought it was a dream! We did it!

899
01:02:17,567 --> 01:02:20,779
草壁先生在吗？电报

900
01:02:21,613 --> 01:02:24,115
草壁先生在家吗？
Mr. Kusakabe? Telegram!

901
01:02:24,115 --> 01:02:26,075
有您的电报
Mr. Kusakabe? Telegram!

902
01:02:26,075 --> 01:02:26,952
Mr. Kusakabe?

903
01:02:27,619 --> 01:02:31,164
没人在家啊
A telegram for you.

904
01:02:31,331 --> 01:02:34,125
Huh. No one's home.

905
01:02:35,752 --> 01:02:40,006
婆婆
(TRAMPLING)

906
01:02:40,173 --> 01:02:44,636
我在这儿
MEI: Granny!

907
01:02:45,679 --> 01:02:48,598
长成这个样就能吃了
I'm over here.

908
01:02:49,808 --> 01:02:52,102
This one's ready to eat.

909
01:02:52,477 --> 01:02:55,021
(GRUNTING)

910
01:02:56,022 --> 01:02:58,608
婆婆，那这个呢？
(SNAP)

911
01:02:58,650 --> 01:03:02,654
可以
What about this one, Granny?

912
01:03:02,821 --> 01:03:03,780
Try it.

913
01:03:03,905 --> 01:03:05,532
(GRUNTING)

914
01:03:05,699 --> 01:03:09,744
婆婆你的这块田　好像是一座宝山啊
(SNAP)

915
01:03:09,828 --> 01:03:13,623
来，休息一下喘口气
Wow, Granny. Your garden is just like a market.

916
01:03:13,790 --> 01:03:21,631
已经冰透了
We've picked enough, haven't we? Let's take a rest.

917
01:03:21,715 --> 01:03:25,510
那我要吃了
Mmm. Nice and cold.

918
01:03:25,677 --> 01:03:28,263
Mark, get set, go!

919
01:03:32,684 --> 01:03:33,768
好好吃啊

920
01:03:33,852 --> 01:03:35,603
真的呀

921
01:03:35,687 --> 01:03:37,856
这是因为经常被太阳晒
It's delicious.

922
01:03:37,981 --> 01:03:40,713
对身体非常健康的啊
I'm glad you like it. They're very good for you.

923
01:03:40,713 --> 01:03:42,402
对妈妈的身体也有益吗？
They've soaked up lots of vitamins and sunshine.

924
01:03:42,402 --> 01:03:43,987
当然啦
They've soaked up lots of vitamins and sunshine.

925
01:03:43,987 --> 01:03:45,759
只要是　吃了婆婆田里种的东西
- Would they help Mom get better?    - Of course they would.

926
01:03:45,759 --> 01:03:47,761
身体就会好啦
- Would they help Mom get better?    - Of course they would.

927
01:03:47,761 --> 01:03:51,181
这个星期六　我妈妈就会回来了
If your mom eats my vegetables, I bet she'd get well right away.

928
01:03:51,181 --> 01:03:53,684
妈妈要跟我一起睡觉啊
That's great, Granny. Mom's coming home on Saturday.

929
01:03:53,684 --> 01:03:55,811
是吗？　马上就要出院了
That's great, Granny. Mom's coming home on Saturday.

930
01:03:55,811 --> 01:03:56,979
She's going to sleep with me in my bed.

931
01:03:56,979 --> 01:03:59,127
不算是真正的出院
Oh, good! She's finally leaving the hospital, is she?

932
01:03:59,127 --> 01:04:01,129
星期一还得回去复诊
Oh, good! She's finally leaving the hospital, is she?

933
01:04:01,129 --> 01:04:03,214
还没有那么快好
No. The doctor wants her to get used to the new house a little at a time.

934
01:04:03,214 --> 01:04:05,133
这样吗？
No. The doctor wants her to get used to the new house a little at a time.

935
01:04:05,133 --> 01:04:07,864
那可要多吃点东西补一补了
- She goes back on Monday.    - Is that so?

936
01:04:07,864 --> 01:04:11,035
我要把我自己摘的　粟米给妈妈吃
We'll feed her lots of my vegetables while she's here.

937
01:04:11,035 --> 01:04:14,976
那她一定会很高兴的
I'll give her the corn that I picked. That will make her better.

938
01:04:15,143 --> 01:04:18,355
- I bet that will do her wonders.    - Yep.

939
01:04:22,275 --> 01:04:23,193
电报

940
01:04:23,276 --> 01:04:24,652
你们不在　所以邮差送去我家

941
01:04:24,736 --> 01:04:28,406
给我们的
Here. The postman left us your telegram.

942
01:04:28,573 --> 01:04:32,619
婆婆　我爸爸不到傍晚不回来
A telegram?

943
01:04:32,702 --> 01:04:36,664
快打开看吧　要是急事耽搁就不好了
What should I do with it, Granny? Dad won't be home till evening.

944
01:04:36,831 --> 01:04:39,063
Better open it. Might be an emergency.

945
01:04:39,063 --> 01:04:42,796
发电处七国山医院
Mmm-hmm.

946
01:04:42,879 --> 01:04:44,839
七国山医院送来的
“Please contact Shichikokuyama.”

947
01:04:44,839 --> 01:04:46,799
那就是从妈妈的医院
“Please contact Shichikokuyama.”

948
01:04:46,799 --> 01:04:48,009
难道妈妈发生了什么事
“Please contact Shichikokuyama.”

949
01:04:48,009 --> 01:04:50,657
Shichikokuyama! It's from Mom's hospital!

950
01:04:50,657 --> 01:04:51,867
婆婆，怎么办？
Something must have happened to her.

951
01:04:51,867 --> 01:04:52,972
医院要我们跟他们联络
Something must have happened to her.

952
01:04:52,972 --> 01:04:54,578
你别紧张，冷静一点

953
01:04:54,578 --> 01:04:56,851
知不知道爸爸上班的地方？
We have to get to the hospital right away, Granny.

954
01:04:56,851 --> 01:04:58,728
爸爸研究室的电话号码　我是知道
Okay. Calm down. First, we need to get in touch with your father.

955
01:04:58,728 --> 01:05:00,271
可是没有电话可打呀
Okay. Calm down. First, we need to get in touch with your father.

956
01:05:00,271 --> 01:05:04,692
勘太　你带小月去打电话
I know his phone number at the university, but we don't have a phone.

957
01:05:04,692 --> 01:05:08,363
Kanta, take Satsuki to your uncle's house and let her use the phone.

958
01:05:08,530 --> 01:05:12,742
小美妳留下来陪婆婆
Mmm-hmm.

959
01:05:14,035 --> 01:05:17,288
Mei, you need to stay here with me!

960
01:05:21,709 --> 01:05:28,550
小美妳回去婆婆那里
Mei, go back and stay with Granny!

961
01:05:36,891 --> 01:05:38,518
Uh!

962
01:06:00,874 --> 01:06:03,835
请你接市外电话

963
01:06:04,711 --> 01:06:08,840
请接东京31局1382号
Hello? I'd like to place a long-distance call, please.

964
01:06:08,840 --> 01:06:11,759
好
It's to my dad at Tokyo 31-13-82.

965
01:06:11,759 --> 01:06:14,846
这个女孩还真是讨人喜欢呢
Right.

966
01:06:15,263 --> 01:06:19,601
喂！是的
Now, that's a nice girl, eh, Kanta?

967
01:06:19,601 --> 01:06:20,205
(RINGS)

968
01:06:20,205 --> 01:06:22,332
请问是考古学教室吗？
Hello?

969
01:06:22,332 --> 01:06:23,062
Yes.

970
01:06:23,062 --> 01:06:25,273
我爸爸⋯　麻烦请草壁先生听电话
Hello? I need to speak to my dad in the archaeology department.

971
01:06:25,273 --> 01:06:27,629
我叫做草壁月
Hello? I need to speak to my dad in the archaeology department.

972
01:06:27,629 --> 01:06:29,903
I mean, I need to speak to Mr. Kusakabe.

973
01:06:30,069 --> 01:06:33,781
爸爸，是我，小月
My name is Satsuki Kusakabe.

974
01:06:33,823 --> 01:06:38,036
怎么了？
Hello, Dad? Is that you? It's Satsuki.

975
01:06:38,203 --> 01:06:40,579
医院来电报？我知道了
- Satsuki, what's wrong?    - We got a telegram.

976
01:06:40,579 --> 01:06:42,707
爸爸现在就　打电话到医院去问
You're supposed to call Mom's doctor at the hospital.

977
01:06:42,790 --> 01:06:44,626
是不是妈妈出事了
What? The hospital?

978
01:06:44,626 --> 01:06:45,752
怎么办呀？爸爸
Okay. I'll call them right away.

979
01:06:45,752 --> 01:06:46,857
不会有事的
Okay. I'll call them right away.

980
01:06:46,857 --> 01:06:49,797
爸爸给医院打过电话　就马上就回妳电话
Did something happen to her, Dad? Do you think she's okay?

981
01:06:49,881 --> 01:06:52,195
你在那边等一下
Let's not worry.

982
01:06:52,195 --> 01:06:54,281
I'll call the hospital, and then I'll call you right back. Okay?

983
01:06:54,281 --> 01:06:56,679
待会儿就打给妳
- Yeah.    - Just wait by the phone.

984
01:06:56,679 --> 01:06:59,807
婆婆　我还可以在这里待一会吗？
- Mmm-hmm.    - I need to hang up now. Okay?

985
01:06:59,849 --> 01:07:01,726
我爸爸还会打电话来

986
01:07:01,768 --> 01:07:05,688
没关系，慢慢来
Excuse me, is it okay if I wait here? My dad says he's going to call me back.

987
01:07:05,813 --> 01:07:08,441
Of course. Make yourself at home.

988
01:07:11,653 --> 01:07:17,951
姊姊
Satsuki!

989
01:07:18,117 --> 01:07:19,244
(PANTING)

990
01:07:21,704 --> 01:07:24,186
不可以啦
(BLEATING)

991
01:07:24,186 --> 01:07:26,542
这个是要给妈妈的粟米
(BLEATING)

992
01:07:26,542 --> 01:07:28,190
不可以！
Back off! Don't touch my corn!

993
01:07:28,190 --> 01:07:29,462
这个是要给妈妈的啦
It's for my mommy!

994
01:07:29,462 --> 01:07:31,047
这个是要给妈妈的啦
(BLEATING)

995
01:07:31,214 --> 01:07:34,717
Too bad! She needs it to make her better.

996
01:07:35,510 --> 01:07:36,844
(BLEATING)

997
01:07:45,895 --> 01:07:46,854
小美

998
01:07:47,605 --> 01:07:49,691
爸爸说妈妈的病又有点恶化了

999
01:07:49,774 --> 01:07:53,152
所以这个礼拜妈妈不能回家了
Mei, the doctor said that Mom's not doing well.

1000
01:07:53,152 --> 01:07:54,758
我不要！
So she doesn't get to come home this weekend.

1001
01:07:54,758 --> 01:07:56,447
你不要也不行啊
So she doesn't get to come home this weekend.

1002
01:07:56,447 --> 01:07:59,325
妈妈要是勉强出院　反而更严重了那怎么办
No fair!

1003
01:07:59,534 --> 01:08:00,827
我不要！
It can't be helped, Mei.

1004
01:08:00,952 --> 01:08:03,037
不过是晚几天而已
What if she came home early, and it made her even worse?

1005
01:08:03,037 --> 01:08:04,914
不过是晚几天而已
It's not fair!

1006
01:08:04,914 --> 01:08:05,915
我不要！

1007
01:08:06,291 --> 01:08:09,168
那妈妈死掉　也没有关系是不是
Mei, we just have to wait a little longer.

1008
01:08:09,168 --> 01:08:10,774
不要！
- No!    - You want her to die, Mei?

1009
01:08:10,774 --> 01:08:12,922
妳这个大笨蛋！
- No!    - You want her to die, Mei?

1010
01:08:12,964 --> 01:08:16,009
我不管妳了！
- Is that what you want?    - No!

1011
01:08:16,217 --> 01:08:18,845
You're such a baby! Just grow up!

1012
01:08:23,891 --> 01:08:27,687
走吧
(SNIFFLING)

1013
01:08:29,856 --> 01:08:32,254
姊姊大坏蛋！
Come on, Mei.

1014
01:08:32,254 --> 01:08:34,506
姊姊大坏蛋！
(CRYING)

1015
01:08:34,506 --> 01:08:37,822
She's so mean!

1016
01:08:38,323 --> 01:08:41,284
(CRYING)

1017
01:09:00,678 --> 01:09:01,721
衣服该收收了

1018
01:09:01,763 --> 01:09:04,682
别这么沮丧

1019
01:09:04,682 --> 01:09:07,893
婆婆不是过来帮忙了吗
Come on, girls. Let's put the laundry away.

1020
01:09:07,893 --> 01:09:12,231
打起精神
Oh, don't be sad. Granny's here to help.

1021
01:09:15,860 --> 01:09:19,906
你爸爸说他今天　要留在医院过夜

1022
01:09:19,906 --> 01:09:23,743
妳妈妈不过是感冒而已
Don't worry. Your father is going to stop by the hospital.

1023
01:09:23,743 --> 01:09:27,955
下个星期六一定会回来的
The doctors say your mom just has a cold.

1024
01:09:28,122 --> 01:09:32,919
之前也是这样
She should be home next Saturday.

1025
01:09:33,669 --> 01:09:35,776
医生说只要住数天就会好了

1026
01:09:35,776 --> 01:09:38,153
而且那次也是说得了感冒
This is just like last time.

1027
01:09:38,153 --> 01:09:41,886
我妈妈要是死了该怎么办
They said Mom just had a little cold, she'd be home in a few days.

1028
01:09:42,678 --> 01:09:43,596
小月

1029
01:09:43,596 --> 01:09:45,577
我妈妈要是死了那我们⋯
Granny, what will we do if she dies?

1030
01:09:45,577 --> 01:09:47,767
我妈妈要是死了那我们⋯
Satsuki!

1031
01:09:48,101 --> 01:09:49,956
Maybe she's dead already.

1032
01:09:49,956 --> 01:09:53,189
妳放心，不要乱想
(CRYING)

1033
01:09:53,189 --> 01:09:57,527
妳妈妈哪舍得下　妳们这些可爱的孩子
Now, don't say that, sweetheart.

1034
01:09:57,527 --> 01:10:01,697
别哭了别哭了
How could she ever leave such sweet girls like you?

1035
01:10:01,697 --> 01:10:03,887
在妳爸爸回来之前
Oh, don't cry.

1036
01:10:03,887 --> 01:10:06,452
婆婆都会陪着妳的　好不好呀
Don't cry. It's all right.

1037
01:10:06,619 --> 01:10:10,123
I'll stay here until your father comes home. Okay? Okay?

1038
01:10:47,827 --> 01:10:55,001
小美呀
Mei!

1039
01:10:55,668 --> 01:10:57,879
小美

1040
01:10:59,922 --> 01:11:02,884
小美
Mei!

1041
01:11:04,635 --> 01:11:06,762
小美回来了没？
Mei!

1042
01:11:06,846 --> 01:11:09,619
没在公车站牌那边吗？

1043
01:11:09,619 --> 01:11:11,809
这就奇怪了
- Did she come back?    - No.

1044
01:11:11,809 --> 01:11:14,395
她会跑到哪里去了？
- She wasn't at the bus stop?    - No.

1045
01:11:14,395 --> 01:11:15,896
我刚刚跟小美吵了一架
Let's think.

1046
01:11:15,896 --> 01:11:18,044
因为她⋯
Do you know anywhere else she might have gone?

1047
01:11:18,044 --> 01:11:21,464
她会不会　跑去妈妈住的医院了
I yelled at her this morning. She wanted Mom to come home.

1048
01:11:21,464 --> 01:11:23,779
七国山医院去了呀
Granny, I bet she went to see Mom at the hospital!

1049
01:11:23,779 --> 01:11:26,073
可是就连大人也得　走上三个钟头才会到
Granny, I bet she went to see Mom at the hospital!

1050
01:11:26,073 --> 01:11:27,199
You think she'd try to walk to the hospital?

1051
01:11:27,199 --> 01:11:30,202
我去看看
Why, that's a three-hour walk even for grown-ups.

1052
01:11:30,202 --> 01:11:33,748
勘太　快点去叫你爸爸回来
I'll go look.

1053
01:11:33,789 --> 01:11:37,502
小美不见了
Kanta! Hurry! Run on home and get your father!

1054
01:11:37,627 --> 01:11:40,546
Mei's disappeared, and we need all the help we can get!

1055
01:11:44,967 --> 01:11:52,558
小美真是笨蛋　不知道路又爱乱跑
I shouldn't have yelled at her. This is all my fault.

1056
01:11:55,811 --> 01:12:02,693
小美
Mei!

1057
01:12:05,071 --> 01:12:08,032
打搅了，伯伯，请问⋯

1058
01:12:08,783 --> 01:12:11,848
您有没有看见束辫子的小女孩　从这条路经过
Excuse me, mister! Hello!

1059
01:12:11,848 --> 01:12:13,850
她是我妹妹
- Yeah?    - I'm looking for my sister.

1060
01:12:13,850 --> 01:12:15,477
这个嘛⋯小女孩啊
- Yeah?    - I'm looking for my sister.

1061
01:12:15,477 --> 01:12:17,792
没什么印象
Did you happen to see a little girl pass this way?

1062
01:12:17,792 --> 01:12:20,190
没什么印象
Let's see. Uh, a little girl?

1063
01:12:20,190 --> 01:12:24,298
她会不会没往这边来
Mmm, I don't think so. I would have noticed.

1064
01:12:24,423 --> 01:12:25,842
I'll try the other road.

1065
01:12:41,148 --> 01:12:43,109
妳确定她是往这边来的？

1066
01:12:43,192 --> 01:12:47,488
我也不知道
MAN: Are you sure that this is the way she came?

1067
01:12:47,655 --> 01:12:49,156
I don't know.

1068
01:12:53,536 --> 01:13:00,084
小美
Mei!

1069
01:13:01,002 --> 01:13:03,588
(HEAVY BREATHING)

1070
01:13:07,884 --> 01:13:10,303
(PANTING)

1071
01:13:16,225 --> 01:13:18,769
停车！
(CAR APPROACHING)

1072
01:13:21,022 --> 01:13:22,398
搞什么啊！危险啊
Stop! Please, stop!

1073
01:13:22,398 --> 01:13:23,774
我在找我妹妹
Stop! Please, stop!

1074
01:13:23,858 --> 01:13:25,672
你们有没有看一个小女孩

1075
01:13:25,672 --> 01:13:27,799
妳妹妹？
- Oh! Are you crazy?    - I'm looking for my little sister.

1076
01:13:27,799 --> 01:13:30,197
她好像是往七国山医院去了
Have you seen a girl walking this way?

1077
01:13:30,197 --> 01:13:31,803
她是一个四岁的小女孩
Is she lost?

1078
01:13:31,803 --> 01:13:34,264
良子啊，妳刚才有没有看到
I think she's trying to walk to the hospital. She's only four years old.

1079
01:13:34,264 --> 01:13:36,412
我们两个　就是从那个方向来的
I think she's trying to walk to the hospital. She's only four years old.

1080
01:13:36,412 --> 01:13:39,206
不过　好像没有看到那样的小孩
Oh. I didn't see her. Did you?

1081
01:13:39,206 --> 01:13:41,458
谢谢你们
No. We just came from the hospital,

1082
01:13:41,458 --> 01:13:44,462
她从哪里来的？
and there was no sign of a little girl on the road.

1083
01:13:44,629 --> 01:13:45,796
松乡
Okay. Thanks.

1084
01:13:45,796 --> 01:13:46,964
松乡！？
Okay. Thanks.

1085
01:13:47,089 --> 01:13:49,800
会不会搞错了呀
- Wait. Where'd you say you're from?    - From Matsugo.

1086
01:13:49,842 --> 01:13:52,094
就是啊
Matsugo! Ho!

1087
01:13:52,094 --> 01:13:54,347
就是啊
A four-year-old couldn't walk this far.

1088
01:13:54,472 --> 01:13:55,431
(ENGINE STARTS)

1089
01:13:55,598 --> 01:13:57,391
MAN: Good luck. I hope you find her.

1090
01:14:03,314 --> 01:14:05,232
小月

1091
01:14:06,359 --> 01:14:09,153
勘太
Satsuki!

1092
01:14:09,737 --> 01:14:10,529
怎么样？

1093
01:14:10,696 --> 01:14:12,969
没看到，那妳呢？
Kanta!

1094
01:14:12,969 --> 01:14:14,825
现在我爸爸他们也去找了
- Find her?    - No.

1095
01:14:14,825 --> 01:14:17,411
我去往七国山的路上看看
- I guess you didn't, either.    - Mmm-mmm.

1096
01:14:17,411 --> 01:14:19,434
妳先回家去
My dad's got a bunch of people looking for her.

1097
01:14:19,434 --> 01:14:20,831
我想小美一定是想去医院
I could ride my bike to the hospital for you.

1098
01:14:20,831 --> 01:14:22,291
可是却走错路了
I could ride my bike to the hospital for you.

1099
01:14:22,291 --> 01:14:24,502
一定是
- You should go back home.    - Check all around.

1100
01:14:24,502 --> 01:14:25,690
刚才有人在神池　发现一只小孩的凉鞋
- You should go back home.    - Check all around.

1101
01:14:25,690 --> 01:14:27,797
I'm sure that Mei got lost on her way to the hospital, okay?

1102
01:14:27,964 --> 01:14:30,758
A little while ago, they found a sandal in the pond.

1103
01:14:33,719 --> 01:14:36,555
不过还不确定　那就是小美的鞋子
(GASPS)

1104
01:14:37,890 --> 01:14:40,851
They don't know for sure it's Mei's sandal!

1105
01:14:51,654 --> 01:14:54,949
找到了吗？
(BREATHING HARD)

1106
01:14:57,660 --> 01:14:59,328
Did you find her yet?

1107
01:15:23,477 --> 01:15:24,895
MAN: We'll check the irrigation ditch.

1108
01:15:25,062 --> 01:15:27,981
喃呒阿弥陀佛
(PEOPLE CHATTERING)

1109
01:15:27,981 --> 01:15:30,901
喃呒阿弥陀佛
MAN: On the far end.

1110
01:15:30,943 --> 01:15:35,009
池那边泥比较深一点　从那边开始啊
(CHANTING)

1111
01:15:35,009 --> 01:15:38,701
递根竹竿给我！
It's much deeper over there. You should try there first!

1112
01:15:38,868 --> 01:15:40,327
MAN: Are there more poles?

1113
01:15:44,707 --> 01:15:49,670
喃呒阿弥陀佛　婆婆，小月来了
(CHANTING)

1114
01:15:49,795 --> 01:15:50,755
(CLAMORING)

1115
01:15:50,921 --> 01:15:53,674
婆婆
Huh?

1116
01:15:53,674 --> 01:15:56,886
妳看看这个
WOMAN: It's Satsuki.

1117
01:15:58,637 --> 01:16:00,723
Here. Is this Mei's?

1118
01:16:05,686 --> 01:16:12,818
不是小美的
- It's not hers.    - Oh!

1119
01:16:12,943 --> 01:16:14,820
(SIGHS)

1120
01:16:16,989 --> 01:16:18,365
太好了
Ohh…

1121
01:16:18,365 --> 01:16:19,742
太好了
(SIGHS)

1122
01:16:19,784 --> 01:16:23,078
我还以　这是小美的
Oh, thank goodness.

1123
01:16:23,078 --> 01:16:25,414
婆婆就爱穷紧张
I was positively certain that sandal belonged to Mei.

1124
01:16:25,414 --> 01:16:27,604
虚惊一场啊
I was positively certain that sandal belonged to Mei.

1125
01:16:27,604 --> 01:16:29,585
那孩子到底跑到哪去了？
All right. Granny just got carried away.

1126
01:16:29,585 --> 01:16:31,107
再去四处找找
Hey! It's not her sandal!

1127
01:16:31,107 --> 01:16:32,797
快点啊，天要黑了
Hey! It's not her sandal!

1128
01:16:32,880 --> 01:16:34,757
不好意思啊

1129
01:16:34,799 --> 01:16:40,262
大家辛苦你们　再回头去找找好了
All right everyone, I know you've spent a lot of time here already,

1130
01:16:40,429 --> 01:16:42,348
but we still need your help.

1131
01:16:52,191 --> 01:16:53,859
Satsuki!

1132
01:17:06,789 --> 01:17:07,957
求求你们

1133
01:17:07,998 --> 01:17:10,000
把我带去龙猫那里
Please.

1134
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:12,148
我的妹妹走丢了
(PANTING)

1135
01:17:12,148 --> 01:17:13,900
不久天就要黑了
Let me in to see Totoro. Mei's lost.

1136
01:17:13,900 --> 01:17:15,485
她一定在哪里迷了路
Let me in to see Totoro. Mei's lost.

1137
01:17:15,485 --> 01:17:17,508
It's getting dark, and she's out there all alone.

1138
01:17:17,675 --> 01:17:20,052
Please let me in to see him. It's an emergency.

1139
01:17:25,099 --> 01:17:27,268
(BREATHING HARD)

1140
01:17:43,742 --> 01:17:44,660
(THUDDING)

1141
01:17:44,827 --> 01:17:45,828
(SCREAMING)

1142
01:17:45,995 --> 01:17:49,415
大龙猫？
(THUDDING)

1143
01:17:49,582 --> 01:17:50,791
大龙猫
(GASPS)

1144
01:17:50,875 --> 01:17:51,959
我妹妹小美走失了
Totoro!

1145
01:17:52,751 --> 01:17:53,919
我找了好久都找不到

1146
01:17:53,961 --> 01:17:57,360
求求你，帮我找小美好不好
Totoro, Mei's lost. I looked everywhere for her, but I couldn't find her.

1147
01:17:57,360 --> 01:17:59,591
她一定已经吓哭了
Totoro, Mei's lost. I looked everywhere for her, but I couldn't find her.

1148
01:17:59,591 --> 01:18:01,010
Please help me. I have to find her.

1149
01:18:01,010 --> 01:18:05,097
我现在不知道该怎么办好
I'm sure she's scared half to death by now.

1150
01:18:05,264 --> 01:18:07,141
I don't know where else to turn.

1151
01:18:07,308 --> 01:18:09,935
(SOBBING)

1152
01:18:25,409 --> 01:18:27,411
(ROARING)

1153
01:18:43,302 --> 01:18:46,722
(INHALES DEEPLY)

1154
01:18:46,889 --> 01:18:49,642
(ROARING)

1155
01:18:57,733 --> 01:19:04,198
大家都看不到它
(YOWLING)

1156
01:19:06,450 --> 01:19:08,244
No one else can see it, can they?

1157
01:19:38,274 --> 01:19:39,525
Huh?

1158
01:19:55,749 --> 01:19:57,126
FOREST-SWAMP

1159
01:19:57,293 --> 01:20:00,671
CEMETERY-SHRINE

1160
01:20:00,838 --> 01:20:01,672
MEI

1161
01:20:01,880 --> 01:20:05,384
- Mei.    - Mei!

1162
01:20:15,728 --> 01:20:19,773
小美
(LAUGHING)

1163
01:20:20,733 --> 01:20:21,817
GRANNY: Mei!

1164
01:20:21,984 --> 01:20:22,901
(GASP)

1165
01:20:23,068 --> 01:20:24,069
Mei!

1166
01:20:27,740 --> 01:20:33,203
树林开出了一条路了
The trees are parting!

1167
01:20:42,129 --> 01:20:43,505
(BARKING)

1168
01:21:00,814 --> 01:21:05,194
小美
(SIGHS)

1169
01:21:05,361 --> 01:21:08,739
姊姊
SATSUKI: Mei!

1170
01:21:09,948 --> 01:21:12,117
姊姊
Satsuki!

1171
01:21:12,117 --> 01:21:14,286
小美
Satsuki!

1172
01:21:14,453 --> 01:21:17,581
- Where are you?    - Mei!

1173
01:21:23,212 --> 01:21:24,254
小美

1174
01:21:24,296 --> 01:21:26,298
姊姊

1175
01:21:27,800 --> 01:21:30,427
妳这个傻瓜
- Mei!    - Satsuki!

1176
01:21:30,427 --> 01:21:32,304
对不起

1177
01:21:32,513 --> 01:21:37,768
妳是不是想要把粟米　送去医院给妈妈？
- Oh! You're okay.    - I'm sorry.

1178
01:21:38,352 --> 01:21:41,355
Were you trying to take your corn to Mom at the hospital?

1179
01:21:41,522 --> 01:21:42,815
Mmm-hmm.

1180
01:21:42,981 --> 01:21:47,986
〝七国山医院〞
(YOWLING)

1181
01:21:49,696 --> 01:21:52,157
你要送我们去医院吗？
HOSPITAL

1182
01:21:53,909 --> 01:21:56,412
谢谢你
You're going to take us to the hospital?

1183
01:21:58,622 --> 01:21:59,706
Thank you!

1184
01:21:59,873 --> 01:22:01,667
(LAUGHING)

1185
01:22:04,795 --> 01:22:06,964
对不起，只不过是感冒

1186
01:22:07,047 --> 01:22:09,528
医院就擅自决定　发电报给家里了
I'm sorry. I don't know why the hospital sent a telegram.

1187
01:22:09,528 --> 01:22:12,010
那两个孩子一定都很担心我吧
I'm sorry. I don't know why the hospital sent a telegram.

1188
01:22:12,094 --> 01:22:14,033
真是苦了她们了
It's just a cold.

1189
01:22:14,033 --> 01:22:16,473
她们知道你平安就会安心的
I hope it didn't upset the girls too much. I've caused them enough grief already.

1190
01:22:16,473 --> 01:22:18,934
这些年来我们一家四口
I hope it didn't upset the girls too much. I've caused them enough grief already.

1191
01:22:18,934 --> 01:22:20,894
不都这样努力过来的吗？
When they see you're all right, they'll be fine.

1192
01:22:20,894 --> 01:22:22,271
享福之前总得吃点苦啊
When they see you're all right, they'll be fine.

1193
01:22:22,271 --> 01:22:24,189
We'll just wait a little longer for a weekend together.

1194
01:22:24,189 --> 01:22:27,922
她们表面好像没事　可是心里一定很难过
Don't worry. We've made it this far.

1195
01:22:27,922 --> 01:22:31,447
小月越是懂事　就越教人于心不忍
The girls act so strong, but I think it's been harder than they let on.

1196
01:22:31,613 --> 01:22:32,968
是啊
Especially Satsuki.

1197
01:22:32,968 --> 01:22:35,471
出院以后我一定要好好疼她们
- She tries to act so adult.    - That's true.

1198
01:22:35,471 --> 01:22:37,827
让她们尽情耍耍小脾气
- She tries to act so adult.    - That's true.

1199
01:22:37,827 --> 01:22:39,079
I can't wait until I get better.

1200
01:22:39,246 --> 01:22:41,957
When I get home, I'm going to spoil those girls rotten.

1201
01:22:42,124 --> 01:22:43,125
(LAUGHING)

1202
01:22:43,292 --> 01:22:48,172
妈妈在笑
(INAUDIBLE)

1203
01:22:48,255 --> 01:22:52,176
看样子是没事了
Look at Mom. She's laughing.

1204
01:22:52,342 --> 01:22:55,220
- Everything must be okay.    - Yeah.

1205
01:22:58,390 --> 01:23:00,976
我得赶快把身体养好才行

1206
01:23:01,059 --> 01:23:04,980
是啊
I'm going to hurry up and get well!

1207
01:23:05,105 --> 01:23:07,733
That's the spirit. Huh?

1208
01:23:10,485 --> 01:23:13,280
是谁摆的啊？

1209
01:23:13,780 --> 01:23:16,012
怎么啦？
Who left this?

1210
01:23:16,012 --> 01:23:17,576
我好像看到小月和小美坐在那棵松树上笑
(GASPS)

1211
01:23:17,576 --> 01:23:19,411
我好像看到小月和小美坐在那棵松树上笑
What is it?

1212
01:23:19,786 --> 01:23:23,790
搞不好是真的也说不定啊
I thought I saw Satsuki and Mei smiling at us from up in that tree.

1213
01:23:23,874 --> 01:23:25,000
妳看

1214
01:23:25,042 --> 01:23:28,045
〝送给妈妈〞
It sounds crazy, but maybe you did.

1215
01:23:28,962 --> 01:23:31,632
- Look at this.    - “For Mommy.”

1216
01:23:34,259 --> 01:23:37,763
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1217
01:23:37,930 --> 01:23:41,141
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1218
01:23:49,566 --> 01:23:53,195
♪ Who leaves the seeds ♪

1219
01:23:53,362 --> 01:23:56,490
♪ For you to find ♪

1220
01:23:56,657 --> 01:23:59,910
♪ Follow them and you will see ♪

1221
01:24:00,077 --> 01:24:04,456
♪ A treasure there ♪

1222
01:24:04,623 --> 01:24:08,126
♪ Then plant the seeds ♪

1223
01:24:08,293 --> 01:24:11,463
♪ And help them grow ♪

1224
01:24:11,630 --> 01:24:14,883
♪ It may seem like a dream ♪

1225
01:24:15,050 --> 01:24:18,845
♪ Things are not what they seem ♪

1226
01:24:19,012 --> 01:24:21,911
♪ Now begins a new adventure ♪

1227
01:24:21,911 --> 01:24:24,622
谢谢观看
♪ For you ♪

1228
01:24:24,622 --> 01:24:27,437
谢谢观看
♪ And you'll be with Totoro ♪

1229
01:24:27,604 --> 01:24:30,065
♪ Totoro ♪

1230
01:24:30,232 --> 01:24:33,735
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1231
01:24:33,902 --> 01:24:37,239
♪ Living in the forest trees ♪

1232
01:24:37,406 --> 01:24:40,242
♪ For such a very, very long time ♪

1233
01:24:40,409 --> 01:24:44,871
♪ There you'll be with Totoro, Totoro ♪

1234
01:24:45,038 --> 01:24:48,500
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1235
01:24:48,667 --> 01:24:52,212
♪ You only see him When you're very young ♪

1236
01:24:52,379 --> 01:24:56,758
♪ A magical adventure for you ♪

1237
01:24:56,925 --> 01:25:00,637
♪ It's magic for you ♪

1238
01:25:02,306 --> 01:25:05,934
♪ Rain tumbles down ♪

1239
01:25:06,101 --> 01:25:09,104
♪ The bus is late ♪

1240
01:25:09,271 --> 01:25:12,399
♪ Suddenly, a furry white giant ♪

1241
01:25:12,566 --> 01:25:17,029
♪ Is by your side ♪

1242
01:25:17,195 --> 01:25:20,782
♪ Don't be afraid ♪

1243
01:25:20,949 --> 01:25:23,952
♪ Just open wide ♪

1244
01:25:24,119 --> 01:25:27,789
♪ Your umbrella for him ♪

1245
01:25:27,956 --> 01:25:31,335
♪ Watch him play in the rain ♪

1246
01:25:31,543 --> 01:25:34,796
♪ Now begins a new adventure ♪

1247
01:25:34,963 --> 01:25:37,924
♪ For you ♪

1248
01:25:38,133 --> 01:25:39,968
♪ And you'll be with Totoro ♪

1249
01:25:40,135 --> 01:25:42,638
♪ Totoro ♪

1250
01:25:42,804 --> 01:25:46,892
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1251
01:25:47,059 --> 01:25:49,895
♪ And on a moonlit night ♪

1252
01:25:50,062 --> 01:25:52,856
♪ He plays a magic flute in the sky ♪

1253
01:25:53,023 --> 01:25:54,941
♪ There you'll be with Totoro ♪

1254
01:25:55,108 --> 01:25:57,569
♪ Totoro ♪

1255
01:25:57,736 --> 01:26:01,073
♪ Totoro, Totoro ♪

1256
01:26:01,198 --> 01:26:04,826
♪ You only see him When you're very young ♪

1257
01:26:04,993 --> 01:26:09,373
♪ A magical adventure for you ♪

1258
01:26:09,498 --> 01:26:14,503
♪ It's magic for you ♪
